OL,3,CJury retires in trial of husband and
OL,4,Cson accused of manslaughter
OL,6,FJurors in the trial of two men who
OL,7,Fdeny manslaughter following the death
OL,8,Fof their elderly relative have retired
OL,9,Fto consider their verdicts.
OL,11,FRobert Christopher Morgan, 61, and 53-
OL,12,Fyear-old David Holyoak are on trial at
OL,13,FCarlisle Crown Court.
OL,15,FThey each deny a charge of
OL,16,Fmanslaughter which alleges that they
OL,17,Funlawfully killed 71-year-old Dorothy
OL,18,FMorgan ` their respective wife and
OL,19,Fmother ` by gross negligence.
