OL,3,CJury retires in trial of husband and
OL,4,Cson accused of manslaughter
OL,6,FA jury has heard that Mrs Morgan was
OL,7,Fadmitted to the West Cumberland
OL,8,FHospital on 25 January, 2021.
OL,10,FShe was found to be in an emaciated,
OL,11,Fmalnourished and severely dehydrated
OL,12,Fstate, weighed only four-and-a-half
OL,13,Fstones and died on 4 February that
OL,14,Fyear.
