OL,3,CJury retires in trial of husband and
OL,4,Cson accused of manslaughter
OL,6,FOver the course of the past three
OL,7,Fweeks, a jury has heard detailed
OL,8,Fevidence in the case. A pathologist
OL,9,Fconcluded the cause of Mrs Morgan's
OL,10,Fdeath was emaciation and neglected
OL,11,Finfected pressure ulcers.
OL,13,FEarlier this week, prosecution and
OL,14,Fdefence lawyers in the case delivered
OL,15,Fclosing arguments before Her Honour
OL,16,FJudge Goddard KC gave legal directions
OL,17,Fand summed up the evidence.
