OL,6,FJurors retired to consider their
OL,7,Fverdicts this morning (14 February),
OL,8,Fand have been told by the trial judge
OL,9,Fthat only verdicts on which all 12 of
OL,10,Fthem are agreed will be considered at
OL,11,Fthis stage of their deliberations.
